description:
The other Vice President at Misumaru Middle School; she`s an honor student who always goes by the rules. Daughter of the Shrine Priest at the local Tenmo Shrine, Nayuta is very serious, almost to a fault. She has trouble expressing her emotions, and doesn`t like the idea of depending on anyone else.
Source: shingu.rightstuf.com
name: Moriyama Nayuta
